  -H "Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>" \
  -F "excel_file=@path/to/excel/file.xlsx" \
  -F "duty_free_type=lotte"
```

#### 2. ì´ë¯¸ì§€ OCR ì²˜ë¦¬
```bash
